#: ../srcs/generated/cymel.main.rst:2
msgid "cymel.main"
msgstr "cymel.main"

#: cymel.main:1 of
msgid "UI以外の全機能。"
msgstr "All functions except UI."

#: cymel.main:3 of
msgid "以下が全て並列に展開され簡単にアクセスできる。"
msgstr ""
"All of the following are expanded in parallel and can be easily accessed."

#: cymel.main:5 of
msgid "現在のセレクションを表す `~.ModuleForSel.sel` や `~.ModuleForSel.selection` 。"
msgstr ""
"`~.ModuleForSel.sel` or `~.ModuleForSel.selection` representing the current "
"selection."

#: cymel.main:6 of
msgid "cymel.core 以下の全て（主要なノードクラスや、データタイプなど）。"
msgstr "Everything below cymel.core (major node classes, data types, etc.)."

#: cymel.main:7 of
msgid "全てのノードクラスにアクセス可能な ``nt`` （ `.NodeTypes` のインスタンスの別名）。"
msgstr ""
"``nt`` (another name for an instance of `.NodeTypes`) that has access to all"
" node classes."

#: cymel.main:8 of
msgid ""
"Maya新旧バージョン互換のためのノードタイプ名マップ ``cntm`` ( `.CompatNodeTypeMap` のインスタンスの別名）。"
msgstr ""
"Node type name map ``cntm`` (another name for instances of "
"`.CompatNodeTypeMap`) for compatibility with new and old versions of Maya."

#: cymel.main:9 of
msgid "cymel.constants の全て。"
msgstr "All about cymel.constants."

#: cymel.main:10 of
msgid "cymel.pyutils 以下の全て。"
msgstr "Everything below cymel.pyutils."

#: cymel.main:11 of
msgid "cymel.utils 以下の全て。"
msgstr "Everything under cymel.utils."

#: cymel.main:12 of
msgid "cymel.initmaya の全て。"
msgstr "Everything about cymel.initmaya."
